{"meta": {"centerNodeId": "taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus", "centerNodeType": "taxonomy", "generatedAt": "2026-05-28T16:28:22", "includedNodeCount": 3, "includedLinkCount": 2, "layoutMode": "precomputed-static"}, "center": {"id": "taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus", "name": "Balsas screech owl", "type": "taxonomy"}, "nodes": [{"id": "taxonomy-genus-megascops", "name": "Megascops", "latinName": "Megascops", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "genus", "summary": "Megascops（Megascops）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联22种鸟类，如Bare-shanked screech owl、Whiskered screech owl、White-throated screech owl等22种鸟类。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 22, "x": -89.3, "y": -635.52, "z": -8.84}, {"id": "bird-balsas-screech-owl-d262be67", "name": "Balsas screech owl", "englishName": "Balsas screech owl", "latinName": "Megascops seductus", "type": "bird", "status": "LC", "summary": "The Balsas screech owl (Megascops seductus) is a species of owl in the family Strigidae. It is endemic to Mexico. Taxonomy and systematics The Balsas screech owl is monotypic. Description The Balsas screech owl is among the larger members of genus Megascops; it is 24 to 27 cm (9.4 to 10.6 in) long and weighs between 150 and 174 g (5.3 and 6.1 oz). Its facial disc is grayish brown with brownish markings and a darker border. Its \"ear\" tufts are short. The crown and upperparts are also grayish brown; the crown has darker streaks and the upperparts have a pinkish blush and dark streaks and other marks. The closed wing shows two bands of whitish spots. The underparts are paler than the upperparts and have narrow dark streaks and faint vermiculation. Distribution and habitat The Balsas screech owl is endemic to interior southwestern Mexico. Its range is centered on the valley of the Balsas River from southern Jalisco southeast into central Guerrero. It inhabits arid open and semi-open areas such as deciduous woodland with cactus, thorn forest, and secondary forest. It can also be found in tropical scrublands and the edges of cultivated areas. In elevation it ranges from 600 to 1,500 m (2,000 to 4,900 ft). Behavior Feeding Like most other screech owls, the Basas screech owl is nocturnal. Its hunting methods have not been described, but its diet apparently includes insects, other arthropods, and small vertebrates. Breeding Very little is known about the Balsas screech owl's breeding phenology. It is assumed to nest in cavities in trees and cacti like others of its genus. Vocalization Both sexes of the Balsas screech owl perform a territorial song described as \"a rather loud series of gruff notes accelerating to a trill ('bouncing-ball' rhythm), book-book-bokbokbobobobrrrrr\". A possible courtship song is \"a series of gruff, screaming 'whinny' trills\". Status The IUCN has assessed the Balsas screech owl as being of Least Concern. Until 2014 it had been considered Near Threatened. However, its population is unknown and is suspected to be in decline due to habitat loss and degradation. References External links Balsas Screech Owl photo gallery VIREO", "shortSummary": "The Balsas screech owl (Megascops seductus) is a species of owl in the family Strigidae. It is endemic to Mexico.", "locations": ["次生林"], "habitats": ["灌丛"], "threats": ["栖息地破坏"], "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/85/Megascops_seductus_99384227.jpg/960px-Megascops_seductus_99384227.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-megascops", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-megascops", "species": "taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus"}, "expandable": true, "x": -354.58, "y": 454.16, "z": -365.03}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus", "name": "Balsas screech owl", "latinName": "Megascops seductus", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "Balsas screech owl（Megascops seductus）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联1种鸟类，如Balsas screech owl。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 1, "x": -354.58, "y": 454.16, "z": -382.43}], "links": [{"key": "bird-balsas-screech-owl-d262be67__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus", "source": "bird-balsas-screech-owl-d262be67", "target": "taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-megascops", "source": "taxonomy-species-megascops-seductus", "target": "taxonomy-genus-megascops", "relation": "belongs_to_genus", "label": "属于属", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 分类字段补充：Balsas screech owl 属于属 Megascops。"}]}
